{{Vgname|日落|en=Sunset}}是比利时[[Tale_of_Tales|Tale of Tales]]制作的第一人称探索游戏，2015年5月推出。游戏设定于虚构国家Anchuria，玩家扮演加百列·奥尔加特的非裔美国女管家安杰拉。

== 玩法 ==

《日落》采用第一人称视角。安杰拉·伯恩斯在日落前一小时干许多家务。她做家务时发现关于文明战争的更多信息，以及正进军的独裁者。随着时间流逝，她发现房间和窗外的城市都发生变化。

== 开发 ==

《日落》于2015年5月21日在全球Microsoft Windows、OS X和Linux推出<ref name="spy">{{cite web|url = http://www.digitalspy.com/gaming/review/a648429/sunset-review-a-war-story-that-lets-you-evoke-your-inner-voyeur.html#~pdl3Ar35EN1nfI|title = Sunset review: A war story that lets you evoke your inner voyeur|last = Donnelly|first = Joe|work = [[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]]|date = 2015-05-20|accessdate = 2015-05-21|archive-date = 2015-10-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151010040116/http://www.digitalspy.com/gaming/review/a648429/sunset-review-a-war-story-that-lets-you-evoke-your-inner-voyeur.html#~pdl3Ar35EN1nfI|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

《日落》由比利时公司[[Tale_of_Tales|Tale of Tales]]开发，公司宣布开发从2014年3月开始<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.vg247.com/2014/03/14/sunset-in-development-at-tale-of-tales-for-linux-mac-and-pc/|title = Sunset in development at Tale of Tales for Linux, Mac and PC|last = Nunneley|first = Stephany|work = [[VG247|VG247]]|date = 2014-03-14|accessdate = 2015-05-21|archive-date = 2018-10-02|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181002123612/https://www.vg247.com/2014/03/14/sunset-in-development-at-tale-of-tales-for-linux-mac-and-pc/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。《日落》从2014年7月14日开始，通过[[Kickstarter|Kickstarter]]举行为期一月的集资；公司计划募资2.5万美金，但最终获得6.7636万<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.polygon.com/2014/7/17/5912599/tale-of-tales-sunset-kickstarter-successful|title = Tale of Tales' Sunset ends with more than double its funding goal on Kickstarter|last = Corriea|first = Alexa Ray|work = [[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]]|date = 2014-07-17|accessdate = 2015-05-21|archive-date = 2016-03-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304075216/http://www.polygon.com/2014/7/17/5912599/tale-of-tales-sunset-kickstarter-successful|dead-url = no}}</ref>。唯一的延伸目标是更多关于主人公安杰拉·伯恩斯的，包括为玩家带来其她长相概念的反射图像。安杰拉的灵感来自[[安吉拉·戴维斯|安吉拉·戴维斯]]和[[妮娜·西蒙|妮娜·西蒙]]<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.polygon.com/2014/6/26/5843918/sunset-stretch-goal-kickstarter-tale-of-tales|title = Why the only stretch goal in Sunset is the chance to see its heroine|last = Farokhmanesh|first = Megan|work = [[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]]|date = 2014-06-26|accessdate = 2015-05-21|archive-date = 2018-08-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180808172012/https://www.polygon.com/2014/6/26/5843918/sunset-stretch-goal-kickstarter-tale-of-tales|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

原声由曾为《[[旅途|旅途]]》作曲的[[奥斯丁·温特里|奥斯丁·温特里]]配乐<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.pcgamer.com/luxuria-superbia-studio-tale-of-tales-goes-to-kickstarter-with-sunset-a-first-person-war-game-without-guns/|title = Luxuria Superbia studio Tale of Tales announces Sunset, a first-person war game without guns|last = Chalk|first = Andy|work = [[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]|date = 2014-06-16|accessdate = 2015-05-21|archive-date = 2020-09-26|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200926225632/https://www.pcgamer.com/luxuria-superbia-studio-tale-of-tales-goes-to-kickstarter-with-sunset-a-first-person-war-game-without-guns/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

